// ============================================================================
// === QUESTIONS DATA: SCENARIOS =============================================
// ============================================================================
// This file defines all of the scenario data used by the Scenario Debug Tracker.
// Each scenario represents a "ticket" or interactive debugging case.
// ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
// ⚠️ IMPORTANT:
//   • This file MUST load BEFORE game-logic.js in your HTML.
//   • The engine reads the window.SCENARIOS object to dynamically build the UI.
